#: maxframe.learn.contrib.lightgbm.classifier.LGBMClassifier.__init__:3 of
msgid ""
"'gbdt', traditional Gradient Boosting Decision Tree. 'dart', Dropouts "
"meet Multiple Additive Regression Trees. 'rf', Random Forest."
msgstr ""
"'gbdt'，传统的梯度提升决策树。'dart'，Dropouts 与多加性回归树的结合。'rf'"
"，随机森林。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.lightgbm.classifier.LGBMClassifier.__init__:7 of
msgid "Maximum tree leaves for base learners."
msgstr "基学习器的最大叶子节点数。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.lightgbm.classifier.LGBMClassifier.__init__:9 of
msgid ""
"Maximum tree depth for base learners, <=0 means no limit. If setting this"
" to a positive value, consider also changing ``num_leaves`` to ``<= "
"2^max_depth``."
msgstr ""
"基学习器的最大树深度，<=0 表示无限制。如果设置为正值，还应考虑将 ``num_"
"leaves`` 修改为 ``<= 2^max_depth``。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.lightgbm.classifier.LGBMClassifier.__init__:12 of
msgid ""
"Boosting learning rate. You can use ``callbacks`` parameter of ``fit`` "
"method to shrink/adapt learning rate in training using "
"``reset_parameter`` callback. Note, that this will ignore the "
"``learning_rate`` argument in training."
msgstr ""
"提升学习率。您可以使用 ``fit`` 方法中的 ``callbacks`` 参数，通过 ``reset_"
"parameter`` 回调在训练中缩小/调整学习率。注意，这样做将忽略训练中的 ``"
"learning_rate`` 参数。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.lightgbm.classifier.LGBMClassifier.__init__:17 of
msgid "Number of boosted trees to fit."
msgstr "拟合的提升树的数量。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.lightgbm.classifier.LGBMClassifier.__init__:19 of
msgid "Number of samples for constructing bins."
msgstr "用于构建分箱的样本数量。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.lightgbm.classifier.LGBMClassifier.__init__:21 of
msgid ""
"Specify the learning task and the corresponding learning objective or a "
"custom objective function to be used (see note below). Default: "
"'regression' for LGBMRegressor, 'binary' or 'multiclass' for "
"LGBMClassifier, 'lambdarank' for LGBMRanker."
msgstr ""
"指定学习任务及相应的学习目标，或使用自定义目标函数（见下文说明）。默认值"
"：LGBMRegressor 为 'regression'，LGBMClassifier 为 'binary' 或 '"
"multiclass'，LGBMRanker 为 'lambdarank'。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.lightgbm.classifier.LGBMClassifier.__init__:25 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Weights associated with classes in the form ``{class_label: weight}``. "
"Use this parameter only for multi-class classification task; for binary "
"classification task you may use ``is_unbalance`` or ``scale_pos_weight`` "
"parameters. Note, that the usage of all these parameters will result in "
"poor estimates of the individual class probabilities. You may want to "
"consider performing probability calibration (https://scikit-"
"learn.org/stable/modules/calibration.html) of your model. The 'balanced' "
"mode uses the values of y to automatically adjust weights inversely "
"proportional to class frequencies in the input data as ``n_samples / "
"(n_classes * np.bincount(y))``. If None, all classes are supposed to have"
" weight one. Note, that these weights will be multiplied with "
"``sample_weight`` (passed through the ``fit`` method) if "
"``sample_weight`` is specified."
msgstr ""
"以 ``{class_label: weight}`` 形式指定类别的权重。此参数仅用于多分类任务；"
"对于二分类任务，可以使用 ``is_unbalance`` 或 ``scale_pos_weight`` 参数。"
"请注意，使用这些参数会导致对各个类别概率的估计较差。您可能需要考虑对模型"
"进行概率校准 (https://scikit-learn.org/stable/modules/calibration.html)。"
"'balanced' 模式会根据输入数据中类别的频率自动调整权重，公式为 ``n_samples"
" / (n_classes * np.bincount(y))``。如果为 None，则假定所有类别的权重为 1"
"。请注意，如果指定了 ``sample_weight``，这些权重将与通过 ``fit`` 方法传递"
"的 ``sample_weight`` 相乘。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.lightgbm.classifier.LGBMClassifier.__init__:37 of
msgid ""
"Minimum loss reduction required to make a further partition on a leaf "
"node of the tree."
msgstr "在树的叶节点上进一步划分所需的最小损失减少量。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.lightgbm.classifier.LGBMClassifier.__init__:39 of
msgid "Minimum sum of instance weight (Hessian) needed in a child (leaf)."
msgstr "子节点（叶节点）所需的实例权重（Hessian）之和的最小值。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.lightgbm.classifier.LGBMClassifier.__init__:41 of
msgid "Minimum number of data needed in a child (leaf)."
msgstr "子节点（叶节点）所需的最小数据量。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.lightgbm.classifier.LGBMClassifier.__init__:43 of
msgid "Subsample ratio of the training instance."
msgstr "训练实例的子采样比例。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.lightgbm.classifier.LGBMClassifier.__init__:45 of
msgid "Frequency of subsample, <=0 means no enable."
msgstr "子采样的频率，<=0 表示不启用。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.lightgbm.classifier.LGBMClassifier.__init__:47 of
msgid "Subsample ratio of columns when constructing each tree."
msgstr "构建每棵树时的列子采样比例。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.lightgbm.classifier.LGBMClassifier.__init__:49 of
msgid "L1 regularization term on weights."
msgstr "权重上的 L1 正则化项。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.lightgbm.classifier.LGBMClassifier.__init__:51 of
msgid "L2 regularization term on weights."
msgstr "权重上的 L2 正则化项。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.lightgbm.classifier.LGBMClassifier.__init__:53 of
msgid ""
"Random number seed. If int, this number is used to seed the C++ code. If "
"RandomState or Generator object (numpy), a random integer is picked based"
" on its state to seed the C++ code. If None, default seeds in C++ code "
"are used."
msgstr ""
"随机数种子。如果为整数，则用于为 C++ 代码生成种子；如果为 RandomState 或 "
"Generator 对象（numpy），则根据其状态选择一个随机整数作为 C++ 代码的种子"
"；如果为 None，则使用 C++ 代码中的默认种子。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.lightgbm.classifier.LGBMClassifier.__init__:58 of
msgid ""
"Number of parallel threads to use for training (can be changed at "
"prediction time by passing it as an extra keyword argument).  For better "
"performance, it is recommended to set this to the number of physical "
"cores in the CPU.  Negative integers are interpreted as following "
"joblib's formula (n_cpus + 1 + n_jobs), just like scikit-learn (so e.g. "
"-1 means using all threads). A value of zero corresponds the default "
"number of threads configured for OpenMP in the system. A value of "
"``None`` (the default) corresponds to using the number of physical cores "
"in the system (its correct detection requires either the ``joblib`` or "
"the ``psutil`` util libraries to be installed).  .. versionchanged:: "
"4.0.0"
msgstr ""
"用于训练的并行线程数（在预测时可以通过额外的关键字参数进行更改）。为了"
"获得更好的性能，建议将其设置为 CPU 中物理核心的数量。负整数将按照 joblib "
"的公式 (n_cpus + 1 + n_jobs) 解释，与 scikit-learn 类似（例如 -1 表示使用"
"所有线程）。值为 0 时对应系统中为 OpenMP 配置的默认线程数。``None``（"
"默认值）表示使用系统中的物理核心数（正确检测需要安装 ``joblib`` 或 ``"
"psutil`` 工具库）。  .. versionchanged:: 4.0.0"

