#: maxframe.learn.contrib.lightgbm.classifier.LGBMClassifier.__init__:85 of
msgid ""
"A custom objective function can be provided for the ``objective`` "
"parameter. In this case, it should have the signature ``objective(y_true,"
" y_pred) -> grad, hess``, ``objective(y_true, y_pred, weight) -> grad, "
"hess`` or ``objective(y_true, y_pred, weight, group) -> grad, hess``:"
msgstr ""
"可以为 ``objective`` 参数提供自定义目标函数。在这种情况下，其签名应为 ``"
"objective(y_true, y_pred) -> grad, hess``，``objective(y_true, y_pred, "
"weight) -> grad, hess`` 或 ``objective(y_true, y_pred, weight, group) -> "
"grad, hess``："

