#: maxframe.learn.contrib.lightgbm.classifier.LGBMClassifier.__init__:94 of
msgid ""
"The predicted values. Predicted values are returned before any "
"transformation, e.g. they are raw margin instead of probability of "
"positive class for binary task."
msgstr ""
"预测值。预测值在任何变换之前返回，例如对于二分类任务，它们是原始边际值而"
"不是正类的概率。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.lightgbm.classifier.LGBMClassifier.__init__:97 of
msgid "weight"
msgstr "权重"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.lightgbm.classifier.LGBMClassifier.__init__:98 of
msgid "The weight of samples. Weights should be non-negative."
msgstr "样本的权重。权重应为非负数。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.lightgbm.classifier.LGBMClassifier.__init__:99 of
msgid "group"
msgstr "组"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.lightgbm.classifier.LGBMClassifier.__init__:-1 of
msgid "numpy 1-D array"
msgstr "numpy 一维数组"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.lightgbm.classifier.LGBMClassifier.__init__:100 of
msgid ""
"Group/query data. Only used in the learning-to-rank task. sum(group) = "
"n_samples. For example, if you have a 100-document dataset with ``group ="
" [10, 20, 40, 10, 10, 10]``, that means that you have 6 groups, where the"
" first 10 records are in the first group, records 11-30 are in the second"
" group, records 31-70 are in the third group, etc."
msgstr ""
"分组/查询数据。仅用于排序学习任务。sum(group) = n_samples。例如，如果你有"
"一个包含100个文档的数据集，并且 ``group = [10, 20, 40, 10, 10, 10]``，这"
"意味着你有6个组，前10条记录属于第一组，第11到30条记录属于第二组，第31到70"
"条记录属于第三组，以此类推。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.lightgbm.classifier.LGBMClassifier.__init__:105 of
msgid "grad"
msgstr "梯度"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.lightgbm.classifier.LGBMClassifier.__init__:106 of
msgid ""
"The value of the first order derivative (gradient) of the loss with "
"respect to the elements of y_pred for each sample point."
msgstr "每个样本点上损失函数相对于 y_pred 元素的一阶导数（梯度）的值。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.lightgbm.classifier.LGBMClassifier.__init__:108 of
msgid "hess"
msgstr "海森矩阵"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.lightgbm.classifier.LGBMClassifier.__init__:109 of
msgid ""
"The value of the second order derivative (Hessian) of the loss with "
"respect to the elements of y_pred for each sample point."
msgstr "每个样本点上损失函数相对于 y_pred 元素的二阶导数（海森矩阵）的值。"

#: maxframe.learn.contrib.lightgbm.classifier.LGBMClassifier.__init__:112 of
msgid ""
"For multi-class task, y_pred is a numpy 2-D array of shape = [n_samples, "
"n_classes], and grad and hess should be returned in the same format."
msgstr ""
"对于多分类任务，y_pred 是一个形状为 [n_samples, n_classes] 的 numpy 二维"
"数组，grad 和 hess 应以相同格式返回。"

